<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrīmatparamagaṁbhīrasyādvādāmōghalāṁchanaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> jīyāttrailōkyanāthasya śāsanaṁ jinaśāsanaṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīśakavarṣa 1409 neya parābhava saṁvatsarada kārttika śuddha pāḍya Ādityavāradallū tribhuvanacūḍāmaṇi Eṁba caityālaya 
<lb n="2" break="no"/><unclear>da ke</unclear>ḷagaṇa neleya bhavaṁtiya paścimadikkinalū paṁḍitadēvara nirūpa halaru seṭṭikārara Anujñeyiṁ kottoṁpaḷe baḷiya cauṭa guṁmaṭaseṭṭi tana tamma birumuseṭṭiyavaru yirisida dēhārakke kallaṁbeṭṭinalū pāriśvadēvara dēvasvadalū baḍagaṇa keṟeya
<lb n="3"/>keḷagaṇa hosa gaddegaḷu 2 yeraḍa ṟanubha<supplied reason="omitted">va</supplied>diṁda nityanaivēdyadēvapūjeyū Ācaṁdrārkkasthāyiyāgi naḍavahāṁge māḍi koṭṭa dharmmaśāsana <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> varddhatāṁ jainaśāsanaṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

